{
  "stem": "23832.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And people had a notion, when they go behind the river, where the Soviets will stop and the Germans will come from the other side of the river.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to [INAUDIBLE], to a town where Mimi was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But did I tell you that I was in the estate?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this midwife, she gave me to stay with her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Remember, I told you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she was, that time, married and she gave birth to twins, a girl and a boy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said to me-- and I had in my mind who I am, in fact.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One day she said to me-- and this woman, the owner of the estate that I took care of her baby-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Leznicka, her name was.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said to midwife, she was going-- she was expecting another child, and she called the midwife to come to deliver the baby.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, when I was in the-- in the woods with this lady that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that she let me stay temporary.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was another friend of my sister's, and she let me stay for 10 days until I had my papers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, what happened, it's her summer house, and her mother's summer house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she wouldn't let me get onto the balcony because she's afraid of her mother, that they'll inform.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had to stay not to show my face to her mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how people were afraid of one another.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't trust one another-- their own mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Polish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just me, not anybody else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I looked at her dog and I said, you see?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
